snippet.title: JSRFMP v0.4.2 Release Teaser
snippet.description:
Tried my hand at making a trailer kinda video for the big update coming out May 5th. I'm not too good at making videos like this, but I hope this gets some of you excited to try it out.

You can download and play it here.
https://gamejolt.com/games/JSRFMP/336004
